title: ‘The Challenge: Spies, Lies, and Allies’ Episode 4 With Justina Valentine | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
Johnny Bananas invites ‘The Challenge: Champs vs. Stars’ runner-up and ‘Wild ’n Out’ star Justina Valentine to get into all the details of Episode 4 of ‘The Challenge: Spies, Lies, and Allies’ (0:30). They talk about Kyle’s big mistake in the daily challenge (26:00), the most intense elimination of the season (59:30), Hughie getting himself in trouble in nominations (1:07:30), and who will be the first domino to fall in the vet alliance.
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guest: Justina Valentine
Associate Producer: Sasha Ashall
Additional Production: Juliet Litman
